  "texts": [
    "The phase sequences embedded in FH waveforms were optimized by Eedara et al. [157] to ensure the same correlation between different waveforms.",
    "In addition, Zhang et al. [158] developed a calibrated matched filter based on subspace projection to handle RSM.",
    "Nonetheless, the receive signal processing for radar-centric ISAC systems is still in its infancy and requires more effort to delve into.",
    "Communication-centric ISAC techniquesIn general, the communication-centric ISAC systems have modified the existing communication waveforms with high design flexibility for target acquisition.",
    "Consequently, communication-centric waveform design is an important component."
  ]
